news.title: Bihar government lifts curbs on building heights in urban areas

news.title: Development, RERA authorities must check construction quality from start of realty project: FPCE
news.para: ​FPCE, an apex body for home buyers, has demanded that development authorities and regulators under RERA should monitor the construction quality from the beginning of a project to fulfil their responsibilities of protecting the interest of home buyers.
